import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.subtract(x1, x0)
    v1 = jnp.minimum(v0, x0)
    v2 = jnp.exp(v0)
    v3 = jnp.cos(v2)
    v4 = jnp.subtract(v1, v3)
    v5 = jnp.exp(x1)
    v6 = jnp.tanh(v4)
    v7 = jnp.tanh(v6)
    v8 = jnp.multiply(v7, v7)
    return v8
